with
  description "You're at the southern end of the large clearing, in front of a small shack made of wood and sheet metal. Behind it, the rock face of the mountain rises, suffocated by an impressive tangle of bushes. You can go in the shack to the west, or back north towards the other end of the clearing.",
  n_to room09,
  w_to room11,
  in_to room11,
has light;

